description: |How to test API endpoints with Clobbr

value: Our devs at Setapp love this app for a reason. Meet Clobbr, a powerful yet easy-to-use tool to load- and speed-test your API endpoints. Clobbr stores your data locally, doesn't require an account, and looks delightful. What more could we ask for?

description: Clobbr Load test API endpoints Clobbr 90 % Mac|

value: Whether you're testing REST, GraphQL, or cloud functions, Clobbr will do the job. Simply enter a URL, tweak the options, and start testing. You can quickly switch between parallel and sequence testing, change the HTTP method, set timeouts and the number of iterations.
